<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.7">
<l>kaṉaiyār kaṭaluṅ karuviḷaiyuṅ kāyāvum</l>
<l>aṉaiyāṉai yaṉpiṉā lārvattā leṉṟum</l>
<l>cuṉaiyār malariṭṭut toṇṭarāy niṉṟu</l>
<l>niṉaiyātār neñceṉṟuñ neñcalla kaṇṭāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The hearts of those who do not meditate, remaining as devotees</l>
<l>Daily offering with love and passion rare flowers from the pools,</l>
<l>To the one who is like the roaring sea, bilva leaves, and kāyā [flowers],</l>
<l>Are never hearts; [this] we have seen.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
